      <title>Enter the Massgrave</title>
      <link>https://deef.dev/posts/massgrave/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 22:58:41 +0200</pubDate>
      <author>deef.deef@gmail.com (Mads)</author>
      <guid>https://deef.dev/posts/massgrave/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s be real. &lt;em&gt;Nobody&lt;/em&gt; likes Windows, and even fewer likes paying for it. Enter the Massgrave.&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;Pirate Flag&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;160&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;160&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png 800w, https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png 1280w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 65vw&#34;&#xA;    data-zoom-src=&#34;https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Howto&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;howto&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#howto&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Copy and paste the code below into your PowerShell terminal:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;irm &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;https&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;py&#34;&gt;activated&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;py&#34;&gt;win&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Follow the prompts and the script will take care of the rest.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;admonition relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg border-l-4 my-3 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm&#34; data-type=&#34;note&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-inherit&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;flex shrink-0 h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center text-lg&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;relative block icon&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 512 512&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M256 0C114.6 0 0 114.6 0 256s114.6 256 256 256s256-114.6 256-256S397.4 0 256 0zM256 128c17.67 0 32 14.33 32 32c0 17.67-14.33 32-32 32S224 177.7 224 160C224 142.3 238.3 128 256 128zM296 384h-80C202.8 384 192 373.3 192 360s10.75-24 24-24h16v-64H224c-13.25 0-24-10.75-24-24S210.8 224 224 224h32c13.25 0 24 10.75 24 24v88h16c13.25 0 24 10.75 24 24S309.3 384 296 384z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;grow&#34;&gt;&#xA;          Note&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;admonition-content mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-inherit&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;irm&lt;/code&gt; command in PowerShell downloads a script from a specified URL, and the &lt;code&gt;iex&lt;/code&gt; command executes it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
